import { Link } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/styles';
import { Box } from '@mui/system';


const useStyle = makeStyles({
  FooterLink: {
    textDecoration: 'none !important',
    color:'white !important', 
    padding: '0px 8px '
    
  }
 

  })
const ListMenu = () => {
  const FooterMenu = useStyle();
  return (
    <Box mt={3}>
      <Link to='/home' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Home
      </Link>
      <Link to='/buy' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Buy
      </Link>
      <Link to='/rent' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Rent
      </Link>
      <Link to='/project' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Projects
      </Link>
      <Link to='/product' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Products
      </Link>
      <Link to='/architect' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Architect
      </Link>
      <Link to='/blogs' className={FooterMenu.FooterLink}>
        Blog
      </Link>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default ListMenu
